Package org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler

Class CustomBaseObject

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler.CustomBaseObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
CustomConfiguration, CustomObjectType, CustomObjectTypeProperty, CustomObjectTypePropertyFlag, CustomObjectTypePropertyItemProperty, CustomObjectTypePropertyItems, CustomProperty, ProvidedProperty
public class CustomBaseObject extends Object
Base object for configuration -> object tree [de]serialization. This object tree is used by the Handlebars template processor to process templates into output files with variable substitution. It is constructed from a JSON configuration file.

    • setIsLast

      public void setIsLast(boolean last)
      Set whether this object is the last in a container of similar objects. This is a helper method for Handlebars to help it decide whether to continue a JSON list (",") or close it ("]" or "}"). It is not set via deserialization of the configuration.
